{"title":"Obed Boundary gravel bike goes lighter with 1×13 Campagnolo Ekar Drivetrain","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/06/09/obed-boundary-gravel-bike-goes-lighter-with-1x13-campagnolo-ekar-drivetrain/","date":1623254039000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p>Obed have dropped a new model of their carbon frame Boundary gravel bike with a 1×13 groupset. The Obed Boundary Campagnolo Ekar is now their top-end model, retailing at $3,995. And, it is the lightest by far, weighing a claimed 18.5 lbs; that’s 0.7 lbs lighter than the 1×11 Shimano GRX 600 model. Here’s more.</p><figure id=\"attachment_261093\" aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-261093\"><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/04095304/Obed-Boundary-Campagnolo-Ekar-Outdoor-Profile.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/04095304/Obed-Boundary-Campagnolo-Ekar-Outdoor-Profile.jpg?ezimgfmt=rs:484x323/rscb18/ng:webp/ngcb18\" alt=\"obed boundary gravel bike campagnolo ekar 1x13\" width=\"1200\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/04095304/Obed-Boundary-Campagnolo-Ekar-Outdoor-Profile.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/04095304/Obed-Boundary-Campagnolo-Ekar-Outdoor-Profile-297x198.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/04095304/Obed-Boundary-Campagnolo-Ekar-Outdoor-Profile-800x533.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/04095304/Obed-Boundary-Campagnolo-Ekar-Outdoor-Profile-120x80.jpg?ezimgfmt=ng:webp/ngcb18 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/06/